casebody.data:
No. 11-564. Florida, Petitioner v. Joelis Jardines. 565 U.S. 1104, 132 S. Ct. 995,

181 L. Ed. 2d 726,

2012 U.S. LEXIS 7. January 6, 2012.

Motion of respondent for leave to proceed in forma pauperis granted. Petition for writ of certiorari to the Supreme Court of Florida granted limited to Question I presented by the petition.

Same case below, 73 So. 3d 34.
